>> source: Reddit + other people
>> time required: 5 minutes
>> servings: 1

Bring water to a boil.

Measure @oolong{2*%g}.

Pour some water into the #teapot and wash the leaves for ~{10%seconds}.

Throw out water. Reboil and pour @water{200*%g} into secondary vessel. Pour this water into the teapot.

Brew for ~{1%minute} on first steep. Brew for ~{30%seconds} on each subsequent one.
